Welcome to the `eightbyten`#index("EightByTen") book template. This template is designed to help you write beautiful technical books using Typst#index("Typst").

== How to Use This Template

1.  *Duplicate the folder*: Copy the `template` folder to start your new project.
2.  *Edit `main.typ`*: Update the `title`, `authors`, and other metadata in the `eightbyten.with(...)` call.
3.  *Add Chapters*: Create new `.typ` files in the `chapters/` directory and include them in `main.typ`.
4.  *Observe*: Use `just watch` to see your changes in real-time.

